exceptions.exn: In environment f : R -> R a, b : R n : nat x : R Hx : a <= x <= b Unable to unify "match unif_part_nat a b n x Hx with | inleft H => Sup_fct f (nth 0 (unif_part a b n) (proj1_sig H)) (nth 0 (a + 1 * (b - a) / (INR n + 1) :: [seq a + INR i * (b - a) / (INR n + 1) | i <- seq.iota 2 n]) (proj1_sig H)) | inright _ => Sup_fct f (nth 0 (unif_part a b n) n) (nth 0 (a + 1 * (b - a) / (INR n + 1) :: [seq a + INR i * (b - a) / (INR n + 1) | i <- seq.iota 2 n]) n) end" with "SF_sup_fun f a b n x".
